<plot>This is a short documentary on the life and films of "The Duke". Instead of using film clips, the producers of this film chose to use trailers from various movies. These include Stagecoach, She Wore a Yellow Ribbon, The Searchers, The Green Berets and several others. Many of Waynes most memorable films including True Grit are only mentioned briefly with occasional production stills.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?278543</url></doc>
